WEBVTT

01:42.970 --> 01:45.990
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:49.000
[Episode 27]

01:51.950 --> 01:52.160
[Yu Bofeng]

01:52.160 --> 01:53.680
[Profile Settings] [Delete]

01:58.070 --> 01:58.729
Hello,

01:58.789 --> 02:00.660
the number you've dialed is unavailable.

02:00.800 --> 02:01.500
Sorry.

02:15.990 --> 02:16.900
Hello, Director Xing.

02:17.579 --> 02:18.320
Yu Zheng.

02:18.670 --> 02:19.740
Drop by the station later.

02:20.030 --> 02:20.680
I have something to discuss.

02:20.710 --> 02:21.110
Okay.

02:25.900 --> 02:28.050
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

02:28.750 --> 02:29.970
How are you two? Are you okay?

02:30.010 --> 02:31.020
We’re fine, Yue.

02:33.150 --> 02:33.660
Captain Jiang.

02:34.250 --> 02:35.740
We've thoroughly investigated

02:35.740 --> 02:36.230
the social network

02:36.270 --> 02:37.500
of the truck driver.

02:37.520 --> 02:38.890
We've tracked down his boss.

02:39.030 --> 02:39.720
But...

02:39.760 --> 02:41.020
the situation is complicated.

02:41.190 --> 02:42.270
Because the person who bribed him

02:42.350 --> 02:43.560
was not his direct boss,

02:43.710 --> 02:44.890
but also under someone else's order.

02:45.070 --> 02:46.400
We need a bit more time.

02:48.130 --> 02:49.220
What about Zhou Zhicheng?

02:49.290 --> 02:50.430
He hasn't stepped out of his house yet.

02:50.470 --> 02:52.090
I've asked my men to keep an eye on him.

02:55.150 --> 02:55.780
Okay.

02:56.150 --> 02:56.870
I'll leave you to it.

03:04.950 --> 03:05.990
Yes, Commissioner Zhao.

03:06.560 --> 03:07.110
I just spoke to

03:07.110 --> 03:08.070
Captain Jia from

03:08.070 --> 03:08.660
Nong'an County,

03:09.230 --> 03:10.620
and I've understood what happened then.

03:10.740 --> 03:11.700
In this matter,

03:11.830 --> 03:13.700
Jiang and Yu did nothing wrong.

03:13.910 --> 03:15.760
The situation now is obvious.

03:16.070 --> 03:16.710
Someone

03:16.750 --> 03:17.940
wants to use this matter

03:18.120 --> 03:19.060
to spread misinformation

03:19.510 --> 03:21.050
on the Internet

03:21.150 --> 03:22.170
and create lies.

03:22.950 --> 03:23.829
Don't worry.

03:24.000 --> 03:24.670
We will handle

03:24.710 --> 03:25.430
this matter well.

03:26.750 --> 03:27.460
Thank you, Commissioner.

03:27.950 --> 03:28.510
Bye.

03:33.470 --> 03:34.150
Come in.

03:35.790 --> 03:36.400
Director Xing.

03:38.100 --> 03:39.290
I've asked

03:39.450 --> 03:40.600
the Cyber Investigation Unit

03:40.630 --> 03:41.230
to look into your case.

03:42.110 --> 03:43.190
We will deal firmly with

03:43.270 --> 03:45.210
those criminals who

03:45.510 --> 03:47.030
spread fraudulent rumors online.

03:47.270 --> 03:48.110
But this matter

03:49.070 --> 03:50.310
will definitely have its impact on you.

03:50.950 --> 03:51.829
You need to be mentally prepared.

03:52.150 --> 03:52.550
Yes.

03:53.530 --> 03:54.600
Sorry, Director Xing.

03:55.170 --> 03:56.570
It's my fault for causing problems

03:57.350 --> 03:58.550
for the force this time.

03:58.870 --> 04:00.150
I asked you here

04:00.170 --> 04:01.360
to tell you that

04:01.830 --> 04:03.730
as long as we do the right thing,

04:03.750 --> 04:05.730
we don't need to be afraid of the rumors.

04:06.610 --> 04:08.210
The Cyber Investigation Unit will be here this afternoon.

04:08.390 --> 04:09.470
You all should connect and sort it out.

04:09.950 --> 04:10.350
Got it.

04:10.390 --> 04:10.790
Okay.

04:11.030 --> 04:11.860
Get back to work.

04:12.790 --> 04:13.190
Okay.

04:13.210 --> 04:14.130
We'll be leaving, Director Xing.

04:18.690 --> 04:22.450
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

04:21.540 --> 04:22.870
How are things going with Yu Bofeng?

04:24.080 --> 04:25.550
He still wouldn't answer my calls.

04:28.670 --> 04:29.340
Yu Zheng.

04:31.020 --> 04:32.300
As your friend,

04:32.830 --> 04:33.670
I'd advise you

04:34.190 --> 04:35.710
to let bygones be bygones.

04:35.830 --> 04:36.510
Don't dwell on it.

04:39.250 --> 04:40.640
Actually after all these years,

04:41.010 --> 04:42.409
I also thought I had let it go.

04:44.110 --> 04:45.520
But when I knew Yu Bofeng

04:45.550 --> 04:47.230
was the adopted son of Wang Dan,

04:47.670 --> 04:48.770
I realized that

04:50.110 --> 04:51.460
this matter

04:51.550 --> 04:52.950
still bothered me greatly.

04:53.510 --> 04:54.230
I understand.

04:55.220 --> 04:55.880
But we

04:55.909 --> 04:57.030
can't change the past.

04:57.710 --> 04:58.670
Let's be in the present.

05:01.550 --> 05:02.120
Captain Jiang.

05:03.350 --> 05:04.350
The Cyber Investigation Unit is here.

05:05.030 --> 05:07.830
[Defending justice, forging the spirit of the police]

05:05.270 --> 05:06.070
Let's go.

05:18.110 --> 05:18.750
Hurry.

05:18.900 --> 05:19.560
Try it.

05:19.560 --> 05:20.330
What is this?

05:21.050 --> 05:22.510
Fish maw chicken soup.

05:22.710 --> 05:23.900
You made it yourself?

05:23.990 --> 05:24.720
Of course.

05:24.750 --> 05:25.350
My goodness!

05:25.390 --> 05:26.030
Let me try it.

05:26.060 --> 05:26.970
Try it.

05:28.850 --> 05:29.560
Look at you.

05:29.590 --> 05:30.860
You finally have a day off,

05:30.950 --> 05:32.380
yet you chose to go shopping with Tang Jie

05:32.430 --> 05:33.370
and even cooked for us.

05:33.470 --> 05:34.150
Pass a bowl.

05:34.150 --> 05:34.680
It's too much.

05:34.700 --> 05:35.909
I feel embarrassed.

05:35.990 --> 05:37.420
I've been stewing this fish maw for a long time.

05:37.550 --> 05:38.150
Try it.

05:38.950 --> 05:40.050
It's stewed to the point it's almost dissolved.

05:40.150 --> 05:40.950
Really?

05:42.490 --> 05:43.390
It's so good.

05:43.409 --> 05:44.150
Isn't it?

05:44.180 --> 05:45.730
But I didn't make it for you two.

05:45.909 --> 05:46.310
Fine.

05:46.320 --> 05:47.960
Let me thank his godmother on behalf of the baby.

05:49.670 --> 05:50.480
It's delicious.

05:50.500 --> 05:51.270
Delicious?

05:51.430 --> 05:52.040
Really?

05:52.120 --> 05:52.790
It's really good.

05:55.110 --> 05:55.710
Well,

05:56.270 --> 05:57.370
what is Jiang busy with?

05:57.390 --> 05:57.950
He has been

05:58.000 --> 05:59.110
very busy recently.

05:59.130 --> 06:00.900
He's working on that case.

06:03.380 --> 06:05.020
Have you tried the chicken?

06:07.570 --> 06:08.340
I'll give you more.

06:08.370 --> 06:09.850
The chicken is tender too.

06:10.680 --> 06:11.980
Here, have some more.

06:12.300 --> 06:13.240
Dalu?

06:14.190 --> 06:14.830
What?

06:16.000 --> 06:16.720
Okay.

06:16.740 --> 06:17.630
I'll be right there.

06:17.790 --> 06:18.430
I'll go over now.

06:18.730 --> 06:19.620
What's wrong?

06:19.750 --> 06:20.440
Something came up at work.

06:20.510 --> 06:21.030
I need to go.

06:21.060 --> 06:21.540
You guys carry on.

06:21.630 --> 06:22.690
What happened?

06:22.940 --> 06:23.850
Well...

06:23.910 --> 06:25.390
We are supposed to start filming, right?

06:25.430 --> 06:26.460
Something's up with the supplier.

06:26.960 --> 06:28.690
At least have a sip.

06:28.860 --> 06:29.390
Yes.

06:29.430 --> 06:30.430
It's Lu Yan's labor of love.

06:30.470 --> 06:31.370
I'll have a sip.

06:34.070 --> 06:34.670
It's good!

06:35.270 --> 06:36.680
Honey, I'll pick you up tonight.

06:36.790 --> 06:37.530
Have fun!

06:37.550 --> 06:38.560
Drive slowly.

06:38.630 --> 06:39.350
Okay, honey.

06:40.420 --> 06:41.150
So busy.

06:41.430 --> 06:42.070
Yeah.

06:44.890 --> 06:46.010
Let's go to the mall after eating.

06:46.030 --> 06:46.960
Buy something with me.

06:47.180 --> 06:48.280
Sure. What are you going to buy?

06:48.670 --> 06:49.950
A lucky wristband.

06:50.870 --> 06:51.510
Okay.

06:56.310 --> 06:57.700
Get the legal department review the contract

06:57.720 --> 06:59.550
and figure out how much we need to pay.

06:59.790 --> 07:00.350
Got it.

07:03.860 --> 07:05.360
I'll get straight to the point.

07:05.710 --> 07:06.640
The art department and setup

07:06.670 --> 07:07.670
have already started work.

07:07.830 --> 07:08.630
Now, Yu Bofeng has

07:08.670 --> 07:09.830
gotten himself into this mess.

07:09.960 --> 07:11.270
Everyone in the production has been asking me if

07:11.270 --> 07:12.010
filming can actually begin.

07:11.930 --> 07:13.010
My phone

07:13.320 --> 07:14.480
has been blowing up.

07:15.620 --> 07:16.500
I'll deal with Bofeng's issue

07:16.520 --> 07:17.920
and suppress it as soon as possible.

07:18.630 --> 07:19.790
If it doesn't work,

07:20.190 --> 07:20.990
I'll change the actor.

07:22.120 --> 07:23.270
Change the actor?

07:24.070 --> 07:25.720
Who else at this level and with an open schedule

07:25.750 --> 07:26.950
would agree to this in just two weeks?

07:27.340 --> 07:28.650
We can't even finish signing the contract.

07:29.770 --> 07:31.080
And that Mr. Ke

07:31.350 --> 07:32.900
is truly doing nothing.

07:32.930 --> 07:33.630
We've worked so hard

07:33.670 --> 07:35.100
during pre-production.

07:35.130 --> 07:36.220
But this old man

07:36.510 --> 07:38.230
comes on set to have fun every day.

07:39.350 --> 07:39.680
How much

07:39.710 --> 07:40.550
did our production pay for him?

07:40.950 --> 07:41.550
Dalu.

07:42.950 --> 07:43.480
Peng.

07:44.460 --> 07:46.020
I know it's not easy for you either.

07:47.000 --> 07:48.340
It's not your fault.

07:48.950 --> 07:50.350
But this project is very important to me.

07:50.470 --> 07:51.870
I cannot let it fail.

07:53.390 --> 07:54.030
I know.

07:54.670 --> 07:55.790
It's definitely my fault when

07:55.830 --> 07:56.830
there's an issue with my artiste.

07:57.990 --> 07:59.659
But I truly didn't expect

07:59.909 --> 08:00.830
the death of Bofeng's foster mother

08:00.850 --> 08:01.810
is related to Jiang Chengyi.

08:01.840 --> 08:03.520
That's completely made up.

08:03.910 --> 08:05.170
I saw it on Weibo.

08:05.350 --> 08:06.320
Something about Jiang Chengyi

08:06.470 --> 08:07.980
shouting at Wang Dan,

08:08.030 --> 08:09.560
and then Yu Zheng pinning him on the ground.

08:09.600 --> 08:10.840
Do you think that's actually possible?

08:11.110 --> 08:12.430
Jiang is a good friend of mine.

08:12.460 --> 08:13.380
I know him well.

08:13.620 --> 08:14.360
He would never

08:14.390 --> 08:15.710
do such a thing.

08:15.790 --> 08:16.710
I suspect somone

08:17.720 --> 08:18.390
is spreading rumors

08:18.430 --> 08:20.020
on purpose.

08:22.270 --> 08:22.750
Could it be

08:22.780 --> 08:23.870
the work of Wang Dan's family?

08:24.220 --> 08:25.860
Who would know such details besides

08:25.920 --> 08:26.940
the family members themselves?

08:27.710 --> 08:28.390
Regardless,

08:28.390 --> 08:29.860
this person is up to no good.

08:30.790 --> 08:31.470
This matter

08:31.540 --> 08:33.110
affects not only our project,

08:33.390 --> 08:34.590
but also Jiang.

08:34.799 --> 08:36.520
So, I'll not back out from the project,

08:36.590 --> 08:38.110
and Jiang will have my full support.

08:41.909 --> 08:42.429
Okay.

08:42.870 --> 08:43.740
Don't worry.

08:43.870 --> 08:45.350
I will solve this problem as soon as possible.

08:45.750 --> 08:46.350
Okay.

08:46.910 --> 08:47.790
I'll wait for your news.

08:53.240 --> 08:54.180
[Huiting Complex]

09:01.300 --> 09:02.260
I'm back.

09:03.760 --> 09:04.380
What are you making?

09:04.540 --> 09:05.510
You're back.

09:05.670 --> 09:06.500
Does it smell good?

09:06.630 --> 09:07.510
Try it.

09:09.350 --> 09:10.150
Here.

09:14.950 --> 09:15.550
How is it?

09:16.550 --> 09:17.810
You didn't add any salt?

09:19.360 --> 09:21.070
Well, Xiao Jie's pregnant, isn't she?

09:21.140 --> 09:22.540
She can't drink anything too salty.

09:23.550 --> 09:25.020
So you weren't making it for me?

09:25.160 --> 09:27.370
Why are you comparing yourself to a pregnant woman?

09:28.030 --> 09:30.050
I'll eat the leftovers of a pregnant woman then.

09:31.860 --> 09:32.860
You...

09:33.430 --> 09:35.110
How have you been today?

09:37.030 --> 09:37.770
Pretty good.

09:38.070 --> 09:38.810
All's normal.

09:44.400 --> 09:45.780
Tell me more.

09:45.830 --> 09:46.870
Share some stories.

09:47.770 --> 09:48.900
You've seen it?

09:50.430 --> 09:51.600
Why didn't you

09:51.670 --> 09:52.480
mention it before?

09:54.260 --> 09:55.570
It happened many years ago.

09:56.110 --> 09:57.240
I was on an assignment.

09:57.350 --> 09:58.200
On the way,

09:58.630 --> 10:01.170
we ran into someone shouting about catching a thief.

10:01.320 --> 10:02.650
So I gave chase.

10:03.580 --> 10:05.170
But I didn't expect that this person

10:05.370 --> 10:06.370
would have a heart attack

10:06.750 --> 10:07.780
and die suddenly.

10:08.310 --> 10:10.140
All this years, I thought

10:10.660 --> 10:11.790
this matter was behind me.

10:12.630 --> 10:14.210
I didn't expect it would return to haunt me.

10:18.030 --> 10:19.640
I mean, isn't it such a coincidence for her to be

10:19.670 --> 10:20.890
Yu Bofeng's foster mother?

10:22.490 --> 10:24.330
You did everything you could.

10:24.380 --> 10:25.750
It's not your fault.

10:33.520 --> 10:34.720
Have you eaten?

10:35.860 --> 10:36.850
Not yet.

10:37.030 --> 10:37.670
I was waiting for you.

10:37.870 --> 10:38.600
Let's eat.

10:38.630 --> 10:39.700
I'll add some salt for you.

10:41.120 --> 10:42.010
Let's eat.

10:45.470 --> 10:45.990
Look.

10:46.490 --> 10:47.190
Isn't it beautiful?

10:47.720 --> 10:48.320
I bought this with Lu Yan

10:48.360 --> 10:49.350
when we were shopping today.

10:49.380 --> 10:49.790
Look.

10:49.830 --> 10:50.990
One for each of us.

10:51.780 --> 10:52.530
Yes, it's nice.

10:52.740 --> 10:53.990
Everything you buy looks good.

10:57.460 --> 10:58.270
Honey,

10:58.960 --> 11:00.440
I've noticed a change in you lately.

11:00.830 --> 11:01.630
No, I don't so?

11:02.590 --> 11:04.500
You used to tell me everything.

11:05.040 --> 11:05.630
But recently,

11:05.670 --> 11:07.300
you seem to have a lot on your mind and

11:07.320 --> 11:08.000
have been speaking less.

11:08.540 --> 11:10.080
I've been busy lately.

11:10.550 --> 11:11.860
I'll be fine after this busy period.

11:12.510 --> 11:13.930
Haven't I told you?

11:14.030 --> 11:15.490
You're pregnant now.

11:15.690 --> 11:17.580
We need to buy a bigger house

11:17.910 --> 11:19.110
and a bigger car,

11:19.410 --> 11:20.780
and also hire a nanny.

11:21.820 --> 11:23.070
I don't want you to take care of our child alone.

11:23.780 --> 11:24.750
It's too tough.

11:27.470 --> 11:28.070
Honey.

11:29.190 --> 11:29.950
Honey!

11:32.440 --> 11:33.710
I know you want to give your all

11:33.750 --> 11:34.720
for our family.

11:35.000 --> 11:36.920
But I'm already very satisfied.

11:37.610 --> 11:39.250
I don't want you to feel burdened.

11:41.840 --> 11:43.070
I'm your wife,

11:43.510 --> 11:45.260
the person closest to you.

11:45.400 --> 11:46.230
If you face any difficulties,

11:46.230 --> 11:47.030
you have to tell me.

11:47.180 --> 11:48.580
You mustn't bear it all alone.

11:48.910 --> 11:49.630
Understand?

11:54.760 --> 11:56.690
I know that Yu Bofeng's trending topic

11:56.720 --> 11:57.510
has greatly affected

11:57.550 --> 11:58.860
your project.

11:59.240 --> 12:00.580
But it will all be resolved.

12:01.510 --> 12:03.090
Don't be upset about this.

12:04.630 --> 12:05.780
Got it, honey.

12:05.940 --> 12:06.600
Cheer up.

12:07.510 --> 12:08.430
Smile.

12:09.600 --> 12:10.570
Smile!

12:32.230 --> 12:32.750
Peng.

12:33.630 --> 12:34.310
Have you eaten?

12:36.840 --> 12:37.830
I have no appetite.

12:38.790 --> 12:40.030
How are things now?

12:43.440 --> 12:44.660
I only have bad news for you.

12:45.470 --> 12:46.600
Which one do you want to hear first?

12:47.280 --> 12:48.400
I'm mentally prepared.

12:49.350 --> 12:49.950
Go ahead.

12:55.330 --> 12:56.460
There are currently 7 endorsements

12:56.550 --> 12:57.680
looking to terminate their contract with you.

12:58.070 --> 12:58.960
We'll have to pay

12:59.220 --> 13:00.310
more than 10 million yuan.

13:01.900 --> 13:02.700
I'll pay.

13:04.110 --> 13:04.640
I'll sell

13:04.670 --> 13:05.740
my house in Yanbei.

13:06.330 --> 13:07.120
It should be enough.

13:07.470 --> 13:08.840
Among your three upcoming projects,

13:09.240 --> 13:11.270
besides the one where I am the main investor,

13:11.370 --> 13:12.750
the other two are also looking to terminate their contracts.

13:12.970 --> 13:14.060
We'll have to pay

13:14.840 --> 13:15.980
about 6 million yuan.

13:17.990 --> 13:19.350
I'll pay with all my savings.

13:20.550 --> 13:22.260
If that's not enough, I'll sell my car.

13:22.750 --> 13:23.710
That should be enough.

13:25.310 --> 13:25.910
Anything else?

13:26.320 --> 13:27.570
Up until now,

13:28.480 --> 13:29.830
your Weibo, Douyin,

13:29.950 --> 13:32.310
and other social media platforms

13:32.510 --> 13:34.440
have lost about 40% of followers collectively.

13:34.470 --> 13:36.610
They all say you have a fake persona.

13:36.750 --> 13:37.790
You're a thief's son.

13:37.870 --> 13:38.710
You lied to the public.

13:44.980 --> 13:45.890
It's okay.

13:46.170 --> 13:47.270
It's not your fault.

13:47.730 --> 13:49.200
You simply kept your background a secret.

13:50.220 --> 13:51.180
Do you understand?

13:56.970 --> 13:57.890
Alright, no matter what,

13:57.920 --> 13:59.080
you still need to eat something.

13:59.230 --> 14:00.030
I'll make you some porridge.

14:07.390 --> 14:07.990
Who is it?

14:12.470 --> 14:13.310
Yu Zheng.

14:15.870 --> 14:16.630
She's looking for you?

14:20.670 --> 14:21.270
Peng.

14:23.230 --> 14:24.070
I'd like to ask you to

14:24.120 --> 14:25.190
help me have a chat Yu Zheng.

14:26.820 --> 14:27.990
I want to know what is

14:28.030 --> 14:29.030
her stance on this matter.

14:30.350 --> 14:31.690
This is very important to me.

14:34.870 --> 14:35.540
Okay.

14:35.950 --> 14:36.920
This way,

14:37.360 --> 14:39.230
we can also avoid unnecessary trouble.

14:44.800 --> 14:49.000
[I'll meet you in my office at 8 a.m. tomorrow]

14:44.800 --> 14:49.000
[Yu Bofeng, at least give me a chance to explain]

14:44.800 --> 14:49.000
[Can we meet and talk?]

14:49.080 --> 14:50.650
[Office]

14:51.190 --> 14:51.750
So he's still

14:51.790 --> 14:52.670
unwilling to see me.

14:54.590 --> 14:55.950
This matter had

14:55.990 --> 14:56.790
hurt him greatly.

14:57.190 --> 14:57.870
He...

14:59.110 --> 15:00.150
still couldn't come.

15:05.280 --> 15:06.010
Professor Yu,

15:08.110 --> 15:09.220
Do you regret it?

15:09.520 --> 15:10.520
She's a thief.

15:11.040 --> 15:12.190
We are the police.

15:13.170 --> 15:14.680
It's only right we arrest her.

15:16.240 --> 15:17.850
What's there to regret?

15:19.610 --> 15:20.960
But it's only

15:20.990 --> 15:22.140
for Bofeng's tuition fees

15:22.160 --> 15:23.310
that she stole the money.

15:23.770 --> 15:25.010
It's just a few hundred yuan.

15:25.230 --> 15:26.280
She didn't deserve to die.

15:26.620 --> 15:27.090
Yes.

15:30.190 --> 15:31.690
That's why I feel guilty.

15:32.950 --> 15:33.710
Otherwise,

15:33.750 --> 15:34.670
I wouldn't have left the frontlines.

15:35.960 --> 15:37.430
I would often think

15:37.830 --> 15:38.720
what if I had

15:38.720 --> 15:39.950
found out about

15:39.980 --> 15:41.770
his mother's health condition earlier,

15:41.800 --> 15:43.640
or had called for an ambulance earlier.

15:43.670 --> 15:45.100
Would things not have become

15:45.190 --> 15:46.190
what it is today?

15:48.870 --> 15:50.140
But it's too late to say anything now.

15:50.350 --> 15:50.990
Isn't it?

15:54.390 --> 15:55.430
As you can see,

15:55.550 --> 15:56.360
the public's opinion

15:56.380 --> 15:57.210
is really getting to Bofeng.

15:58.920 --> 16:00.170
Can you step forward

16:00.560 --> 16:01.790
and make things clear?

16:02.270 --> 16:03.110
Make things clear?

16:05.390 --> 16:06.470
What do you want me to say?

16:08.990 --> 16:10.470
To make clear that Yu Bofeng's mother

16:11.110 --> 16:11.910
is not a thief.

16:16.360 --> 16:17.650
I'm sorry. I can't do that.

16:20.060 --> 16:21.060
Regardless,

16:21.360 --> 16:23.310
from a legal perspective,

16:23.670 --> 16:24.760
Wang Dan had indeed

16:24.790 --> 16:25.750
committed a theft.

16:26.230 --> 16:26.990
Regardless of

16:27.030 --> 16:28.230
whichever identity and stance I assume,

16:28.270 --> 16:29.070
there's no way I can

16:29.110 --> 16:29.910
make such a clarification.

16:30.670 --> 16:32.370
This case has been settled.

16:32.470 --> 16:34.260
There's no wiggle room.

16:34.550 --> 16:35.690
You really think that

16:35.750 --> 16:36.740
with just a few words from me,

16:36.830 --> 16:37.790
you could turn the case around?

16:41.670 --> 16:42.760
Alright, Professor Yu.

16:43.030 --> 16:44.500
I hope you won't meet Bofeng

16:44.590 --> 16:45.630
for the time being.

16:46.130 --> 16:47.970
It's better for everyone.

16:48.150 --> 16:48.630
Okay.

16:52.430 --> 16:53.030
Goodbye.

16:53.900 --> 16:54.510
See you.

17:08.579 --> 17:11.569
[Convert to Text] [Annotate]

17:16.300 --> 17:16.839
Professor Yu.

17:16.510 --> 17:17.869
[Convert to Text] [Annotate]

17:19.060 --> 17:20.089
Do you regret it?

17:20.310 --> 17:21.430
She's a thief.

17:21.960 --> 17:23.250
We are the police.

17:24.099 --> 17:25.630
It's only right we arrest her.

17:25.670 --> 17:27.300
What's there to regret?

17:28.250 --> 17:29.340
Can you step forward

17:29.450 --> 17:30.420
and make things clear?

17:30.750 --> 17:32.710
To make clear that Yu Bofeng's mother

17:32.910 --> 17:33.840
is not a thief.

17:34.280 --> 17:35.680
I'm sorry. I can't do that.

17:39.590 --> 17:40.230
Bofeng.

17:41.470 --> 17:42.590
I know it's hard for you to believe

17:42.610 --> 17:43.530
Yu Zheng's stance.

17:44.830 --> 17:46.310
But that's how some things are.

17:47.060 --> 17:48.310
In this world,

17:48.670 --> 17:49.670
it's not all black or white.

17:53.190 --> 17:54.190
She's already gone.

17:55.390 --> 17:56.510
Don't take it too seriously.

18:03.550 --> 18:04.150
Bofeng.

18:05.510 --> 18:06.390
I'm sorry, Peng.

18:09.870 --> 18:10.510
Please give me

18:10.550 --> 18:11.150
some time to myself.

18:32.040 --> 18:34.240
[Ninghai Public Security Bureau - Statement of clarification regarding Yu Bofeng]

18:34.320 --> 18:38.650
[Ninghai Public Security Bureau - Statement of clarification regarding Yu Bofeng]

18:51.890 --> 18:53.410
Wen Peng came to find me this afternoon.

18:53.510 --> 18:55.530
He wants me to record a video of clarifying that

18:56.000 --> 18:57.630
Yu Bofeng's foster mother

18:57.630 --> 18:58.650
is not a thief.

18:58.830 --> 18:59.910
Isn't he ridiculous?

19:02.220 --> 19:03.990
However, I believe Yu Bofeng

19:04.000 --> 19:05.230
must be really upset this time.

19:05.310 --> 19:06.670
It's difficult to process right away.

19:07.440 --> 19:09.110
But he is also someone

19:09.110 --> 19:10.510
with a lot of mood swings.

19:11.400 --> 19:13.190
Wen Peng is just messing around.

19:13.750 --> 19:14.840
The police will never

19:14.870 --> 19:16.300
tell lies to the public.

19:16.470 --> 19:17.530
Otherwise, there's no credibility left.

19:17.710 --> 19:18.690
Exactly.

19:18.870 --> 19:20.610
There's a call from the station

19:21.280 --> 19:23.010
asking us to assist the Cyber Investigation Unit with a case.

19:23.550 --> 19:24.310
Let's go.

19:24.390 --> 19:24.950
Get in.

19:29.180 --> 19:30.210
Hold on.

19:33.550 --> 19:33.910
What's wrong?

19:33.910 --> 19:34.790
I think I forgot my phone.

19:34.790 --> 19:35.580
Wait for me.

19:35.710 --> 19:36.190
Okay.

19:55.570 --> 19:56.880
Jiang Chengyi, let me ask you.

19:57.370 --> 19:58.150
Back then, did you and Yu Zheng

19:58.150 --> 19:59.070
witness for yourself

19:59.070 --> 20:00.120
Aunt Wang stealing?

20:02.510 --> 20:03.720
A statement

20:04.020 --> 20:05.570
has been made regarding this.

20:05.670 --> 20:07.010
I won't read your statement.

20:07.150 --> 20:07.550
I'm asking you

20:07.550 --> 20:09.250
if you've witnessed it with your own eyes.

20:10.030 --> 20:10.890
No.

20:11.570 --> 20:13.260
But we had a witness

20:13.290 --> 20:14.230
and material evidence.

20:14.710 --> 20:15.950
And in the end, we had also proven that

20:15.990 --> 20:17.310
she did steal something.

20:17.420 --> 20:18.710
Show me the evidence.

20:20.130 --> 20:21.980
If you really want to see it,

20:22.610 --> 20:23.890
I can make a request to the force

20:23.900 --> 20:24.930
and get the materials for you.

20:25.100 --> 20:26.930
Who are you trying to kid?

20:27.070 --> 20:28.060
It's just to fool me.

20:28.960 --> 20:29.710
Don't think I don't know

20:29.710 --> 20:30.390
what you're thinking.

20:30.510 --> 20:31.640
She's dead anyway.

20:31.860 --> 20:32.350
In the end,

20:32.390 --> 20:33.650
it's always up to you guys,

20:33.830 --> 20:34.390
right?

20:35.280 --> 20:37.100
That's not right of you to say.

20:37.410 --> 20:39.650
What's in it for me to

20:40.070 --> 20:41.420
wrong Aunt Wang of stealing money?

20:41.460 --> 20:41.830
Fine.

20:41.880 --> 20:42.950
Even if Aunt Wang had stolen,

20:42.970 --> 20:44.420
it was only 500 yuan.

20:44.450 --> 20:45.630
You drove her to death

20:45.670 --> 20:47.290
over just 500 yuan!

20:49.070 --> 20:50.770
Don't get so worked up.

20:50.920 --> 20:51.730
Calm down.

20:52.550 --> 20:54.120
That's not how it works.

20:54.270 --> 20:55.150
Stealing

20:55.310 --> 20:56.750
is not about the stolen value.

20:56.870 --> 20:57.510
As for me,

20:57.590 --> 20:58.820
I just happened to come across

20:58.870 --> 20:59.960
criminal behavior while on the street.

20:59.990 --> 21:01.170
As a police officer,

21:01.230 --> 21:02.320
could I have just ignored it?

21:02.220 --> 21:03.150
There were no issues

21:03.150 --> 21:04.360
with our actions.

21:05.110 --> 21:06.510
Of course, its certainly unexpected

21:07.530 --> 21:08.460
that something like this happened.

21:09.000 --> 21:10.610
It's not something we want to see either.

21:10.950 --> 21:12.360
We also feel sorry.

21:13.600 --> 21:14.960
Fine. You have regrets, right?

21:15.110 --> 21:16.120
I'll give the police

21:16.140 --> 21:16.820
a chance.

21:17.340 --> 21:18.670
I want the police to clarify that

21:18.710 --> 21:19.970
Aunt Wang is not a thief.

21:23.840 --> 21:25.180
That's not something we can do.

21:30.050 --> 21:31.090
What are you doing?

21:31.800 --> 21:32.850
Calm down.

21:32.870 --> 21:34.410
You're assaulting a police officer, you know?

21:37.090 --> 21:38.060
Calm down!

21:41.260 --> 21:42.200
Yu Bofeng.

21:42.480 --> 21:43.480
Calm down.

21:52.680 --> 21:54.060
Hello, is this 110?

21:54.230 --> 21:55.070
There's a fight here.

21:55.070 --> 21:56.320
Please hurry over!

21:57.310 --> 21:58.080
Calm down!

21:58.590 --> 21:59.650
Calm down!

22:01.340 --> 22:02.250
What are you doing?

22:03.540 --> 22:04.360
Yu Bofeng!

22:05.800 --> 22:06.630
Calm down.

22:06.680 --> 22:07.530
Can you calm down?

22:09.100 --> 22:10.270
Can you calm down?

22:14.790 --> 22:16.640
[Exit]

22:19.870 --> 22:20.510
Get up.

22:25.270 --> 22:26.720
Yu Bofeng, have you gone crazy?

22:26.790 --> 22:27.600
Stop!

22:27.710 --> 22:28.640
Get out of my way!

22:28.750 --> 22:29.220
Stop!

22:29.250 --> 22:29.730
Stop!

22:36.950 --> 22:37.810
What's going on?

22:39.630 --> 22:40.160
Are you okay?

22:40.190 --> 22:40.950
I'm fine.

22:47.950 --> 22:48.590
Bro.

22:50.830 --> 22:51.660
Uh...

22:52.670 --> 22:53.230
His...

22:53.900 --> 22:54.880
family member had passed away.

22:54.910 --> 22:55.770
Hence...

22:57.650 --> 22:58.980
he might have been feeling overwhelmed.

23:03.110 --> 23:03.670
Okay.

23:11.920 --> 23:12.840
Tell me.

23:11.960 --> 23:17.150
[Limin Local Police Station]

23:13.040 --> 23:14.210
What happened?

23:18.620 --> 23:19.610
I'm Yu Zheng.

23:20.710 --> 23:22.100
That's Yu Bofeng.

23:22.540 --> 23:24.670
Jiang Chengyi was the one who had the conflict with him.

23:27.450 --> 23:29.600
I am guessing you might've been busy

23:29.920 --> 23:32.080
and haven't paid much attention

23:32.270 --> 23:33.540
to what happened recently.

23:32.320 --> 23:35.720
[Limin Local Police Station]

23:33.570 --> 23:34.620
Take a look.

23:37.730 --> 23:40.490
[How could the police force someone to death?]

23:37.730 --> 23:40.490
[Yu Bofeng's real identity revealed; Foster mother mistaken as a thief; Dies on the spot]

23:44.430 --> 23:44.950
See,

23:45.390 --> 23:47.200
I guess it all makes sense now, right?

23:47.890 --> 23:49.330
He was just being impulsive.

23:49.650 --> 23:50.310
I am sure

23:50.350 --> 23:51.310
Jiang Chengyi won’t

23:51.330 --> 23:52.410
hold him accountable either.

23:53.150 --> 23:53.870
Could we just...

23:53.870 --> 23:54.910
He might have been impulsive,

23:54.940 --> 23:55.700
but it's different when

23:55.750 --> 23:56.710
he assaulted a police.

23:57.040 --> 23:57.840
We

23:57.900 --> 23:58.920
have also verified.

23:59.110 --> 23:59.860
Jiang Chengyi

23:59.900 --> 24:02.270
was assisting the Cyber Investigation Unit then.

24:02.950 --> 24:04.960
He was officially on call.

24:05.380 --> 24:06.400
The onlookers

24:06.640 --> 24:08.720
had also recorded a video of Yu Bofeng beating him.

24:09.320 --> 24:10.090
We have both

24:10.110 --> 24:10.740
witnesses and also

24:10.770 --> 24:11.440
material evidence.

24:13.010 --> 24:14.030
Yes.

24:14.110 --> 24:19.180
[Limin Local Police Station]

24:14.760 --> 24:16.640
But he's still young.

24:16.670 --> 24:17.900
After something like this happened,

24:17.930 --> 24:19.400
he's constantly being attacked online.

24:19.470 --> 24:20.830
He must be under a lot of pressure.

24:21.160 --> 24:22.510
Under extreme pressure,

24:22.550 --> 24:23.150
people tend to

24:23.160 --> 24:24.220
act irrationally.

24:24.350 --> 24:25.230
He's only 23 years old,

24:25.240 --> 24:26.290
Sir.

24:27.630 --> 24:28.270
Madam.

24:29.490 --> 24:30.960
What's your relationship with him?

24:31.390 --> 24:32.030
He is...

24:34.720 --> 24:35.820
We are friends.

24:37.660 --> 24:38.510
23 years old.

24:39.590 --> 24:40.820
He's an adult now.

24:41.520 --> 24:42.070
He needs to learn

24:42.110 --> 24:43.350
to be responsible for his actions.

24:55.110 --> 24:55.690
Here.

24:55.870 --> 24:56.950
Okay, thank you.

25:03.470 --> 25:04.230
Yu Bofeng.

25:07.880 --> 25:08.840
Don't worry.

25:09.350 --> 25:10.360
Jiang Chengyi said

25:10.390 --> 25:11.480
he won't hold you accountable.

25:13.430 --> 25:14.630
You will be fine.

25:15.480 --> 25:17.240
Don't bother, Professor Yu.

25:19.170 --> 25:21.080
You’re all cut from the same cloth.

25:22.950 --> 25:24.310
You all framed Aunt Wang back then.

25:24.350 --> 25:25.870
Will you all let me go now?

25:28.590 --> 25:29.230
I wonder

25:29.230 --> 25:30.640
what kind of heinous villain

25:30.670 --> 25:32.190
you police will make me

25:32.210 --> 25:33.920
out to be.

25:35.070 --> 25:35.980
What do you mean?

25:41.110 --> 25:41.950
What do I mean?

25:47.710 --> 25:49.150
Didn't you say it yourself?

25:50.320 --> 25:52.160
Regardless of whether Aunt Wang was a thief,

25:52.860 --> 25:54.260
you would label her as one

25:54.950 --> 25:56.230
in order to protect yourselves.

26:17.890 --> 26:19.650
I just talked to

26:19.720 --> 26:20.690
with the chief of Limin Local Police Station.

26:21.240 --> 26:22.640
I am aware of what happened.

26:22.930 --> 26:23.960
Director Xing.

26:24.150 --> 26:26.950
He was really angry then.

26:26.990 --> 26:27.550
And so,

26:28.200 --> 26:29.310
emotions were running high.

26:31.480 --> 26:32.710
The problem is that

26:33.160 --> 26:34.300
it was a citizen who called the police.

26:34.590 --> 26:35.680
There were surveillance cameras at the scene too.

26:36.430 --> 26:37.760
The police is also in a difficult situation.

26:38.150 --> 26:38.790
I understand.

26:39.430 --> 26:40.500
I've also liaised with the officer

26:40.550 --> 26:42.070
who responded to the call.

26:42.990 --> 26:44.050
Regarding this, I'm willing to

26:44.470 --> 26:45.190
provide him with a

26:45.190 --> 26:46.320
letter of forgiveness.

26:46.470 --> 26:48.230
Let's try to downplay the situation and

26:48.270 --> 26:48.990
just let it slide.

26:49.740 --> 26:50.990
It's not easy for him as well.

26:51.390 --> 26:52.000
Alright.

26:52.030 --> 26:52.920
I understand now.

26:53.790 --> 26:55.460
But as the old saying goes,

26:55.750 --> 26:56.830
a mistake is a mistake.

26:56.850 --> 26:58.070
There's still a price to pay.

26:58.350 --> 26:59.300
I understand.

26:59.640 --> 27:00.750
Although what happened before

27:00.790 --> 27:02.320
remains a burden in my heart,

27:02.390 --> 27:03.810
he needs to face the consequences

27:03.950 --> 27:04.950
of his own actions.

27:06.190 --> 27:07.390
If there's nothing else, you can leave now.

27:07.430 --> 27:08.380
Go back and rest for a few days.

27:08.430 --> 27:09.650
Just look at your health.

27:09.460 --> 27:11.850
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

27:09.720 --> 27:10.630
My health's fine.

27:10.710 --> 27:11.710
What could be wrong?

27:11.990 --> 27:12.560
Hurry up.

27:12.590 --> 27:13.230
Go back and rest.

27:13.870 --> 27:14.710
If there's anything,

27:14.830 --> 27:15.900
just call Qin

27:15.930 --> 27:16.650
and tell them.

27:16.910 --> 27:17.980
Hurry, hurry up.

27:18.080 --> 27:19.210
I'll go back first, Director Xing.

27:21.590 --> 27:22.430
Look at you,

27:22.450 --> 27:23.690
walking like a mummy.

27:26.370 --> 27:29.960
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

27:30.270 --> 27:31.650
The patient is 69 years old.

27:31.660 --> 27:32.680
He has chronic illness.

27:33.150 --> 27:34.620
You are still suggesting local anesthesia?

27:35.380 --> 27:35.990
But the patient

27:36.030 --> 27:37.470
is very fearful of surgery.

27:37.500 --> 27:39.380
Even with local anesthesia, she still feels pain.

27:39.860 --> 27:41.140
I'm afraid that if she comes agitated

27:41.160 --> 27:42.030
during the operation,

27:42.190 --> 27:43.270
it could hinder the surgery.

27:43.770 --> 27:46.140
So prior to the surgery, you need to counsel her well.

27:46.170 --> 27:47.430
Have a good chat with her

27:47.450 --> 27:48.600
to calm her down.

27:48.870 --> 27:49.270
Okay.

27:50.200 --> 27:51.030
Lu Yan.

27:51.480 --> 27:52.160
Captain Jiang

27:52.190 --> 27:53.560
is currently receiving treatment in the Emergency Department.

28:02.310 --> 28:03.140
Hi, Sister.

28:03.390 --> 28:04.270
What happened?

28:05.560 --> 28:06.630
His waist is injured,

28:06.670 --> 28:07.980
and his back muscles are inflamed.

28:08.270 --> 28:09.940
Plus, as he's been overworked recently,

28:10.000 --> 28:11.350
he also has acute fasciitis.

28:11.510 --> 28:12.310
It's nothing major.

28:12.340 --> 28:13.400
I'll prescribe some medicine for him.

28:13.940 --> 28:14.540
Thank you.

28:14.640 --> 28:15.030
Rest well.

28:15.060 --> 28:15.690
Okay.

28:16.180 --> 28:16.860
Sister,

28:16.880 --> 28:18.080
let me tell you something.

28:18.640 --> 28:19.680
He wouldn't let me tell you that he was sick.

28:19.700 --> 28:21.000
He told me to keep it from you.

28:21.020 --> 28:22.530
What's that about?

28:22.630 --> 28:23.490
What are you talking about?

28:23.750 --> 28:24.630
You were the one who asked me to hide it.

28:24.650 --> 28:25.470
Stop pretending.

28:26.110 --> 28:26.580
That hurts.

28:28.870 --> 28:30.900
I wasn't hiding it. I just...

28:31.670 --> 28:32.950
It was no big deal,

28:32.970 --> 28:33.480
so I...

28:33.810 --> 28:35.360
I don't want this to affect your work.

28:35.710 --> 28:36.650
You weren't hiding it from me?

28:36.670 --> 28:38.020
If you weren't, why are you lying here?

28:38.410 --> 28:39.850
It was nothing at first,

28:40.190 --> 28:41.800
but Qin Yue insisted to give me a massage.

28:41.960 --> 28:43.260
After that,

28:43.280 --> 28:44.000
I was done for.

28:44.020 --> 28:44.840
Tell me.

28:44.870 --> 28:45.920
What happened?

28:47.030 --> 28:48.970
I got into a bit of a conflict with someone.

28:49.330 --> 28:50.460
With whom?

28:51.730 --> 28:52.760
Yu Bofeng.

28:55.440 --> 28:57.080
Regarding his foster mother?

28:58.620 --> 28:59.070
Yes.

28:59.110 --> 29:01.120
I couldn't get him to understand.

29:01.620 --> 29:02.100
Senior,

29:02.150 --> 29:02.960
take this opportunity

29:02.960 --> 29:03.970
to have a good rest.

29:03.990 --> 29:05.280
Did you hear what he said?

29:05.390 --> 29:05.790
Can you...

29:05.790 --> 29:06.230
Dr. Lu.

29:06.230 --> 29:07.150
Bed No. 3 needs you.

29:09.320 --> 29:10.450
Sister, don't worry.

29:10.590 --> 29:11.230
As long as I'm around,

29:11.250 --> 29:12.520
I will take care of him for you.

29:13.190 --> 29:14.200
You'd better.

29:14.280 --> 29:15.290
Lie down and rest.

29:16.310 --> 29:17.070
Goodbye, Sister.

29:21.430 --> 29:21.990
Senior.

29:22.470 --> 29:23.760
Do you feel like

29:23.780 --> 29:25.460
the two of you are in

29:25.490 --> 29:26.360
better shape lately?

29:27.310 --> 29:28.080
What's changed?

29:28.270 --> 29:29.300
Her spirit and demeanor,

29:29.910 --> 29:30.550
her skin,

29:31.150 --> 29:31.830
and her mood.

29:31.850 --> 29:33.760
People who are nourished by love

29:33.790 --> 29:34.630
are indeed different.

29:35.110 --> 29:36.070
Stop teasing me.

29:36.090 --> 29:37.420
You... go out and have fun.

29:37.510 --> 29:38.680
I want love too.

29:38.700 --> 29:39.580
Go find it.

29:39.600 --> 29:40.990
Ask your girlfriend to introduce someone to me.

29:41.030 --> 29:41.870
This way, we can be hospitalized

29:41.900 --> 29:42.950
together in the future.

29:42.990 --> 29:43.830
Stop talking nonsense.

29:43.870 --> 29:44.620
Go out and find it.

29:44.650 --> 29:45.670
I want love too.

29:45.870 --> 29:46.390
Introduce someone to me,

29:46.430 --> 29:48.100
and we can be hospitalized together.

29:48.350 --> 29:49.520
Stop messing with me.

29:49.790 --> 29:50.470
Rest well.

29:58.830 --> 30:00.510
Go get some physiotherapy tomorrow.

30:01.760 --> 30:02.860
No, I can't.

30:03.030 --> 30:04.470
I’m the most experienced when it comes to this.

30:05.270 --> 30:06.240
If I don't touch it,

30:06.470 --> 30:07.570
the pain is localized.

30:07.880 --> 30:09.180
If I go for therapy,

30:09.310 --> 30:10.350
my entire back will hurt instead.

30:13.230 --> 30:14.670
You won't listen to me.

30:14.350 --> 30:15.940
♫As the city flickers♫

30:15.790 --> 30:16.550
What's wrong with him?

30:16.590 --> 30:17.550
He went hard on you.

30:17.050 --> 30:20.240
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

30:17.990 --> 30:19.570
It's not that he's heavy-handed.

30:19.960 --> 30:20.880
My muscles on this side

30:20.920 --> 30:21.790
were already overworked.

30:21.120 --> 30:22.630
♫And you, who love to smile♫

30:22.400 --> 30:23.850
With just a bit of force,

30:23.430 --> 30:26.020
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

30:23.870 --> 30:25.260
it will easily get inflamed.

30:26.910 --> 30:29.430
♫The humor of time♫

30:26.980 --> 30:28.340
Yu Bofeng

30:29.030 --> 30:29.910
was too impulsive.

30:30.740 --> 30:33.380
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

30:31.300 --> 30:33.260
I made it very clear to him.

30:33.990 --> 30:35.390
He just can't get over it himself.

30:34.260 --> 30:40.490
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

30:35.750 --> 30:36.550
Then,

30:37.830 --> 30:38.990
what'll happen to him?

30:39.870 --> 30:41.540
I will write him a letter of forgiveness.

30:41.400 --> 30:43.240
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

30:42.110 --> 30:43.080
Maybe he'll

30:43.400 --> 30:44.440
get a lighter punishment.

30:44.130 --> 30:47.280
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

30:45.330 --> 30:47.090
Take a good rest at home the next two days.

30:47.150 --> 30:48.390
Make sure to take care of your back.

30:48.270 --> 30:50.000
♫The stubborn me♫

30:48.710 --> 30:49.350
Do you hear me?

30:49.750 --> 30:50.550
I know.

30:50.930 --> 30:53.900
♫I always think of the far future♫

30:52.150 --> 30:53.710
I can't move now anyway.

30:54.420 --> 30:56.730
♫I walk willfully♫

30:56.550 --> 30:57.790
No, don't move.

30:57.860 --> 31:00.930
♫Like a star revolving around♫

30:58.160 --> 30:59.250
H-Help me lie down.

30:59.300 --> 30:59.830
What are you up to?

31:00.020 --> 31:00.740
It's not

31:01.070 --> 31:01.630
comfortable here.

31:01.420 --> 31:02.880
♫I turn around♫

31:02.130 --> 31:03.060
Come, give me a hand.

31:03.350 --> 31:04.030
You...

31:03.900 --> 31:07.650
♫But you're not behind me♫

31:07.510 --> 31:08.070
How am I...

31:08.110 --> 31:08.630
Slow down.

31:08.670 --> 31:09.310
Come on.

31:09.070 --> 31:10.710
♫Losing you♫

31:11.470 --> 31:12.560
♫It's so unreal♫

31:25.090 --> 31:25.660
Mr. Wen

31:28.830 --> 31:29.630
How is it?

31:30.070 --> 31:31.590
He's still in the police station.

31:31.610 --> 31:33.180
It's considered an assault on the police.

31:33.470 --> 31:34.280
Fortunately,

31:34.310 --> 31:35.880
it didn't cause serious consequences.

31:36.480 --> 31:38.290
What's crucial now

31:38.310 --> 31:39.540
is Jiang Chengyi.

31:39.850 --> 31:41.560
If he can forgive him

31:41.590 --> 31:42.950
and downplay the incident,

31:43.230 --> 31:44.590
the best possible outcome

31:44.960 --> 31:45.970
would likely be detention

31:46.110 --> 31:46.910
as a form of punishment.

31:49.810 --> 31:50.360
Mr. Wen.

31:51.010 --> 31:51.920
How about

31:52.390 --> 31:53.910
you talk to

31:54.150 --> 31:55.010
Jiang Chengyi?

31:55.310 --> 31:55.990
What did you say?

31:56.720 --> 31:57.270
No.

31:57.390 --> 31:58.780
I mean...

31:59.100 --> 32:00.590
you guys are college alumni.

32:01.190 --> 32:02.750
If you step in to help,

32:02.790 --> 32:04.070
wouldn't this matter...

32:12.790 --> 32:14.310
Don't make such a low-level mistake again

32:14.330 --> 32:15.320
in the future.

32:16.510 --> 32:17.070
Got it.

32:20.800 --> 32:22.360
I'll use my other contacts.

32:24.180 --> 32:24.830
Okay.

32:47.270 --> 32:48.010
Professor Yu!

32:48.430 --> 32:49.030
Professor Yu!

32:52.060 --> 32:53.090
I made it.

32:57.110 --> 32:57.790
Thank you.

32:59.320 --> 33:00.000
Thank you, Ms. Yu.

33:04.240 --> 33:04.850
I'm leaving.

33:09.200 --> 33:10.360
What now?

33:10.630 --> 33:12.480
While I'm hospitalized...

33:15.290 --> 33:17.060
can you come over and help me catch up on my studies?

33:19.120 --> 33:19.810
Actually, I...

33:22.350 --> 33:23.030
Say no more.

33:23.730 --> 33:24.540
I know.

33:25.100 --> 33:26.020
What do you know again?

33:27.530 --> 33:28.410
You like me.

33:33.370 --> 33:34.520
When I was little,

33:34.540 --> 33:35.380
my mother would also always

33:35.400 --> 33:36.040
give me her egg.

33:38.050 --> 33:38.920
Some more.

33:39.480 --> 33:40.400
Are you sure?

33:40.730 --> 33:41.280
Yes.

34:09.239 --> 34:10.010
Yu Zheng.

34:10.510 --> 34:11.239
Are you asleep?

34:11.330 --> 34:11.889
What's wrong?

34:12.460 --> 34:13.620
How's your back?

34:14.340 --> 34:14.909
I'm fine.

34:14.929 --> 34:15.960
I'll recover in a few days.

34:16.440 --> 34:17.150
You...

34:17.600 --> 34:18.710
Something's up? It's late.

34:21.370 --> 34:22.590
I know it's inappropriate

34:22.610 --> 34:23.620
for me to say this,

34:24.460 --> 34:26.560
but I would like to ask you to

34:26.590 --> 34:27.710
write a letter of...

34:27.730 --> 34:28.840
I understand what you are trying to say.

34:29.500 --> 34:30.530
Actually,

34:30.630 --> 34:31.389
I've mentioned it to the

34:31.409 --> 34:32.610
officer-in-charge back then.

34:34.110 --> 34:35.650
But it's such a big deal now.

34:35.670 --> 34:36.550
I really don't know

34:36.580 --> 34:37.870
how would it all work out.

34:37.900 --> 34:39.190
Yes, I know.

34:39.590 --> 34:40.870
It's quite serious this time.

34:42.949 --> 34:43.960
But it's not easy for him

34:43.989 --> 34:45.000
to come this far either.

34:46.870 --> 34:48.210
Just consider it as a favor for me.

34:48.790 --> 34:49.230
Will you?

34:49.500 --> 34:50.630
Don't worry.

34:51.750 --> 34:52.710
Actually,

34:52.750 --> 34:53.710
the incident back then

34:53.750 --> 34:54.909
had always been a burden in my heart.

34:55.909 --> 34:56.750
I will never

34:56.790 --> 34:57.470
give him a hard time.

34:58.030 --> 34:58.630
Don't worry.

35:00.270 --> 35:00.950
Thank you.

35:01.910 --> 35:02.510
Okay.

35:03.190 --> 35:03.870
Don't worry.

35:04.520 --> 35:06.010
Tell me if you need anything.

35:13.180 --> 35:13.770
Who is it?

35:14.590 --> 35:15.480
Professor Yu.

35:16.220 --> 35:17.150
What's wrong again?

35:17.780 --> 35:19.150
She's worried about Yu Bofeng.

35:19.970 --> 35:20.720
It's fine.

35:20.910 --> 35:22.310
Take off your cardigan and sleep.

35:29.390 --> 35:30.280
Need my help?

35:30.350 --> 35:31.270
It's not that serious.

35:31.350 --> 35:31.910
I'm fine.

35:32.100 --> 35:32.960
I can lie down.

35:34.880 --> 35:36.090
Don't overstretch yourself.

35:37.430 --> 35:37.900
Here.

35:40.740 --> 35:41.530
Done.

35:42.890 --> 35:43.310
Okay.

35:43.330 --> 35:43.910
Okay.

35:43.930 --> 35:44.470
Alright.

35:56.830 --> 35:57.710
Let's sleep.

35:58.030 --> 35:58.760
Yes.

37:01.010 --> 37:01.710
You're awake.

37:03.190 --> 37:04.360
Let me change it for you.

37:07.520 --> 37:08.470
It hurts here?

37:10.650 --> 37:11.440
Are you okay?

37:11.440 --> 37:12.350
Do you need my help?

37:12.720 --> 37:13.940
How will you help with brushing my teeth?

37:13.970 --> 37:14.950
I'll hold it for you.

37:15.900 --> 37:16.990
Why did you swallow it?

37:20.570 --> 37:21.840
Let me carry you back.

37:22.050 --> 37:22.950
It's best if you don't touch me.

37:22.970 --> 37:23.780
Let me hug you.

37:27.180 --> 37:28.110
Why are you looking at me?

37:28.140 --> 37:29.390
I'll see if you can put it on.

37:29.430 --> 37:30.570
Help me.

37:30.920 --> 37:32.340
So you need help now?

37:32.510 --> 37:33.410
Say, "Help me?"

37:33.430 --> 37:34.170
Help me.

37:35.430 --> 37:35.830
Come on.

37:37.630 --> 37:39.110
Don't move so much.

37:39.110 --> 37:39.750
I'll pull it for you.

37:45.280 --> 37:45.750
Okay.

37:48.790 --> 37:50.060
Sleeping again?

37:51.110 --> 37:52.200
I just closed my eyes for a while.

37:53.230 --> 37:53.590
Here.

37:53.610 --> 37:55.140
I bought breakfast for you.

37:55.170 --> 37:55.800
Okay.

37:59.550 --> 38:00.470
Take a look.

38:02.390 --> 38:03.520
Get up and eat.

38:04.880 --> 38:06.610
It's really hard for me to get up from this position.

38:06.710 --> 38:07.270
Give me a hand.

38:07.290 --> 38:08.330
Give you a hand?

38:08.800 --> 38:09.440
Okay.

38:10.800 --> 38:11.430
Here.

38:12.310 --> 38:13.780
How can I help you without causing any pain?

38:13.990 --> 38:15.150
Can't I just hold onto your hand?

38:15.240 --> 38:16.090
Pull me up from my back.

38:16.680 --> 38:17.800
I'll hold you up then.

38:21.500 --> 38:22.870
This is unbearable, honestly.

38:23.320 --> 38:24.630
Get better soon then.

38:27.080 --> 38:28.130
Try this.

38:28.700 --> 38:29.670
I'll get it for you.

38:29.700 --> 38:30.830
Just tell me.

38:30.860 --> 38:31.930
Your mouth's broken too?

38:32.310 --> 38:33.270
I feel embarrassed to trouble you.

38:33.290 --> 38:34.480
You're indeed in a lot of trouble.

38:35.320 --> 38:36.380
Don't take this lightly.

38:36.410 --> 38:37.110
Listen.

38:37.140 --> 38:38.150
With your brute force,

38:38.170 --> 38:39.530
even a little effort

38:39.550 --> 38:40.620
would result in injuring

38:40.670 --> 38:41.790
the same muscle again.

38:42.550 --> 38:43.810
It'll get better in three or four days.

38:43.830 --> 38:44.790
I still have to work.

38:44.820 --> 38:46.380
Three or four days?

38:46.510 --> 38:47.040
No matter what,

38:47.070 --> 38:48.310
you should at least have a week off.

38:48.510 --> 38:50.220
How am I going to work

38:50.350 --> 38:51.310
if I take a week off for this?

38:51.330 --> 38:52.530
Then don't get hurt.

38:54.320 --> 38:55.320
Take a sip.

38:59.850 --> 39:00.760
That's sweet.

39:05.950 --> 39:07.580
I've put the medicine there.

39:07.670 --> 39:08.390
It's painkillers.

39:08.480 --> 39:09.630
When it hurts a lot,

39:09.670 --> 39:10.510
take one more.

39:10.550 --> 39:11.230
It's fine.

39:11.260 --> 39:12.220
I'll try not to eat it.

39:12.250 --> 39:12.850
What for?

39:12.880 --> 39:13.880
It's no big deal, right?

39:14.250 --> 39:15.230
Again?

39:16.220 --> 39:16.790
You say you're fine,

39:16.790 --> 39:17.630
only to get hurt afterwards.

39:17.650 --> 39:18.180
I'm fine.

39:19.530 --> 39:20.920
I'm going to work.

39:21.070 --> 39:21.950
You're on duty?

39:22.590 --> 39:23.830
Wouldn't you want to take care of me

39:23.850 --> 39:24.800
when it hurts the worst these two days?

39:25.660 --> 39:27.230
So I shouldn't take care of my patients in the hospital,

39:27.270 --> 39:27.800
is that right?

39:28.070 --> 39:30.410
Help me to lie back.

39:31.170 --> 39:32.030
You don't want to eat anymore?

39:32.670 --> 39:33.370
I'll eat later.

39:33.390 --> 39:34.700
I can't eat when it hurts this way.

39:34.990 --> 39:35.750
Let me help you.

39:35.780 --> 39:36.570
-Come.
-Come on.

39:41.560 --> 39:43.100
Don't worry. Go to work.

39:43.430 --> 39:44.520
I'm leaving.

39:44.710 --> 39:45.440
I'm fine.

39:55.630 --> 39:56.230
Director Xing.

39:56.800 --> 39:57.560
Director Xing.

39:58.790 --> 39:59.750
Do you think you could

39:59.990 --> 40:01.680
have another word

40:01.690 --> 40:03.830
with the station's chief again?

40:03.910 --> 40:04.590
Well...

40:04.630 --> 40:06.310
I've already sent them the letter of forgiveness.

40:06.710 --> 40:07.950
I've told them everything.

40:07.990 --> 40:08.430
Yes.

40:08.450 --> 40:09.190
As for

40:09.270 --> 40:10.270
how'll this case be settled,

40:11.870 --> 40:12.920
that's beyond my scope to decide.

40:13.710 --> 40:14.680
I know.

40:14.720 --> 40:15.190
But...

40:15.320 --> 40:17.350
Please help me out here.

40:17.380 --> 40:18.960
Please talk to them again.

40:19.110 --> 40:19.750
I've tried my best

40:19.750 --> 40:21.240
to communicate with them.

40:21.270 --> 40:22.280
If I say anymore,

40:22.430 --> 40:23.870
I'll be breaking the rules.

40:26.280 --> 40:27.120
I know

40:27.140 --> 40:28.520
you feel guilty

40:29.180 --> 40:30.630
for what happened

40:30.790 --> 40:31.830
to his foster mother.

40:32.130 --> 40:33.160
But Yu,

40:33.590 --> 40:34.950
haven't you had many cases where

40:35.390 --> 40:36.550
it's a matter of law over mercy?

40:38.070 --> 40:38.940
We can't

40:38.990 --> 40:39.790
lose our judgment

40:40.350 --> 40:41.390
because of our personal emotions.

40:42.420 --> 40:43.990
This matter is final.

40:44.020 --> 40:45.260
You and Jiang

40:45.630 --> 40:46.240
have done

40:46.270 --> 40:47.230
your best.

40:47.660 --> 40:48.630
Wait for my news.

40:48.910 --> 40:50.070
I'll let you know if there's any news.

40:51.390 --> 40:52.550
Okay, thank you, Director Xing.

40:52.730 --> 40:56.580
[Case evaluation room]

41:01.090 --> 41:01.850
Professor Yu.

41:02.800 --> 41:03.920
Relevant information regarding Runying Pictures

41:03.950 --> 41:04.530
are all here.

41:04.840 --> 41:06.210
All the projects, from investment

41:06.230 --> 41:07.280
to co-production and production,

41:07.310 --> 41:08.430
are in place.

41:09.710 --> 41:10.280
Okay.

41:10.870 --> 41:11.470
Thank you.

41:11.500 --> 41:20.670
[Case evaluation room]

41:11.670 --> 41:12.150
You're welcome.

41:26.010 --> 41:26.990
First, it was his fake identity.

41:26.990 --> 41:27.640
That I will say no more.

41:27.680 --> 41:28.810
Now, Yu Bofeng

41:29.110 --> 41:30.050
went on the street

41:30.110 --> 41:31.130
to beat up the police.

41:31.610 --> 41:32.390
Listen.

41:32.410 --> 41:33.590
We must change Yu Bofeng

41:33.590 --> 41:34.310
no matter what.

41:36.570 --> 41:37.270
Peng.

41:37.750 --> 41:39.030
What did Mr. Ke say?

41:41.110 --> 41:42.410
What else?

41:42.750 --> 41:44.910
Regret, anger and fustration.

41:45.350 --> 41:46.460
But Mr. Ke said

41:46.530 --> 41:47.990
we cannot delay the start of production.

41:48.190 --> 41:49.330
He wants us to resolve it as soon as possible.

41:50.060 --> 41:50.880
Otherwise,

41:51.230 --> 41:52.270
he'll give the intellectual property rights to someone else.

41:52.810 --> 41:53.690
No way.

41:54.050 --> 41:55.140
What about the money?

41:58.390 --> 41:59.430
Before you came,

41:59.450 --> 42:00.270
I've contacted

42:00.310 --> 42:01.230
a few top actors.

42:02.160 --> 42:03.350
But the conditions they've proposed

42:03.390 --> 42:04.390
are very tough to meet.

42:05.030 --> 42:05.920
To put it bluntly,

42:06.070 --> 42:07.430
they know we have a problem.

42:07.450 --> 42:08.940
They’re making unreasonable demands now.

42:09.830 --> 42:11.070
But the problem is

42:12.910 --> 42:14.150
I don't have much money to offer.

42:16.450 --> 42:18.230
But most importantly,

42:18.270 --> 42:19.830
pre-production has been all paid for by us.

42:20.150 --> 42:20.920
I know.

42:21.600 --> 42:22.360
I'm also in a

42:22.400 --> 42:23.550
tight spot right now.

42:23.990 --> 42:25.060
As you can see,

42:25.150 --> 42:26.750
the people demanding compensation from me

42:26.770 --> 42:27.910
have started to form a queue.

42:35.630 --> 42:37.030
Actually, to say these things to you both,

42:37.070 --> 42:37.670
I...

42:38.670 --> 42:39.510
I also feel very guilty.

42:39.550 --> 42:40.150
But I...

42:40.710 --> 42:41.930
I really have no choice.

42:47.910 --> 42:48.510
How about this?

42:49.510 --> 42:50.140
Zhong.

42:50.230 --> 42:51.400
I'll give you two choices.

42:52.580 --> 42:54.610
You either pull out,

42:54.790 --> 42:56.210
and then we sign an agreement

42:56.230 --> 42:57.890
where we'll put the money you've invested

42:57.910 --> 42:58.950
into the next film

42:59.030 --> 42:59.750
of my company.

43:01.750 --> 43:02.230
Or,

43:02.960 --> 43:04.260
we think of other ways

43:04.280 --> 43:05.670
and raise some more money

43:06.150 --> 43:07.400
to get a top actor

43:07.430 --> 43:08.550
and ask him to save this production.

43:09.810 --> 43:10.940
What do you think?

43:15.190 --> 43:16.680
Let me think about it.

43:18.240 --> 43:18.930
Okay.

43:19.040 --> 43:20.330
You must decide fast.

43:30.160 --> 43:30.710
Zhong.

43:30.740 --> 43:32.100
What are you still thinking about?

43:32.120 --> 43:33.400
Let's just quit if it doesn't work out.

43:33.630 --> 43:34.310
I heard that they

43:34.330 --> 43:35.000
still have several projects

43:35.030 --> 43:35.770
with the platform.

43:35.800 --> 43:37.130
We can always do something else.

43:38.150 --> 43:38.770
Dalu.

43:38.800 --> 43:40.570
That's not what I'm thinking about.

43:41.410 --> 43:42.670
How many years have we been in this industry?

43:43.060 --> 43:44.380
It's been at least ten years.

43:44.670 --> 43:45.310
Yes.

43:45.920 --> 43:47.480
In this industry, projects have always

43:47.500 --> 43:49.090
followed the actors' availability.

43:49.400 --> 43:51.050
Now that the actor is in trouble,

43:51.070 --> 43:52.350
mormally, the investors

43:52.370 --> 43:53.000
will think long and hard

43:53.020 --> 43:54.020
with the producers.

43:54.590 --> 43:55.020
Yes.

43:55.180 --> 43:56.670
Wen Peng has been in the industry for so many years.

43:56.700 --> 43:57.910
There's no way he doesn't get this.

43:58.170 --> 43:58.790
So why is he

43:58.870 --> 43:59.880
so anxious to start production?

44:01.830 --> 44:03.110
I have a nagging feeling that

44:03.150 --> 44:04.440
something's wrong with Mr. Ke.

44:04.510 --> 44:05.830
Dalu, look into him.

44:06.240 --> 44:07.990
He never seemed like an investor to me.

44:08.350 --> 44:08.790
Okay.

44:08.870 --> 44:09.840
I'll look into it right away.

44:19.110 --> 44:19.710
Hello?

44:20.830 --> 44:21.430
Qin Yue.

44:21.850 --> 44:22.370
Senior.

44:22.640 --> 44:24.680
the Cyber Investigation Unit called.

44:24.700 --> 44:25.830
They said that the individual

44:24.770 --> 44:29.420
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

44:25.880 --> 44:27.530
used virtual currency from a game

44:27.630 --> 44:29.460
as a bait to

44:29.500 --> 44:30.490
lure others into

44:30.630 --> 44:31.750
spreading rumors online.

44:32.420 --> 44:33.280
But this game

44:33.300 --> 44:34.830
is still under beta testing.

44:35.590 --> 44:36.470
There is no registered name yet.

44:36.500 --> 44:37.900
So it will take some time.

44:38.430 --> 44:38.960
Okay.

44:39.740 --> 44:41.690
Something's wrong with that driver, right?

44:43.210 --> 44:44.110
Captain Jiang,

44:44.260 --> 44:45.880
we’ve found the boss.

44:45.740 --> 44:50.070
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

44:46.020 --> 44:46.700
And now,

44:46.730 --> 44:47.570
I've brought him back.

44:47.820 --> 44:49.010
I'll report to you

44:49.040 --> 44:49.970
if I uncover any meaningful leads.

44:50.520 --> 44:51.280
Thank you.

44:51.710 --> 44:52.380
It's okay.

44:52.470 --> 44:53.430
Take care of yourself at home.

44:53.460 --> 44:54.420
Don't worry about us.

44:54.670 --> 44:55.790
If you don't trust these kids,

44:55.830 --> 44:56.790
do you still not trust me?

44:57.790 --> 44:58.310
Okay.

45:02.120 --> 45:03.170
Yu Bofeng.

45:03.870 --> 45:05.040
How was he dealt with?

45:05.980 --> 45:06.790
This morning,

45:06.810 --> 45:07.870
police from Limin Local Police Station

45:07.890 --> 45:08.510
called me.

45:08.550 --> 45:09.760
He said he was detained for five days.

45:09.930 --> 45:10.480
Senior,

45:10.510 --> 45:11.350
your letter of forgiveness worked,

45:11.430 --> 45:12.160
I think.

45:12.840 --> 45:14.160
Okay, go get busy.

45:14.390 --> 45:14.820
Alright.

45:23.620 --> 45:26.660
[and may be detained for assaulting a police officer]

45:23.620 --> 45:26.660
[Yu Bofeng clashed with police officer Jiang Chengyi over his foster mother's case]

46:08.540 --> 46:09.310
Yu Bofeng.

46:10.650 --> 46:12.570
You were arrested for assaulting police officer Jiang Chengyi.

46:12.860 --> 46:13.710
Although in the process

46:13.710 --> 46:14.910
there was no grave consequences,

46:15.400 --> 46:16.670
and Jiang Chengyi

46:16.690 --> 46:18.260
had also forgiven your behavior,

46:19.200 --> 46:20.860
this is still considered an assault on the police.

46:21.090 --> 46:21.950
It has brought about

46:21.950 --> 46:23.270
a serious and adverse influence on society.

46:25.120 --> 46:26.730
According to

46:26.760 --> 46:28.240
Article 43,

46:28.470 --> 46:29.610
Paragraph 1 of

46:29.640 --> 46:30.690
Public Security Administration Punishments Law

46:31.430 --> 46:32.480
of the People's Republic of China,

46:32.500 --> 46:34.460
you will be administratively detained for five days.
